      "message": "Patch Set 1: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(4 inline comments)\n\nI agree that this is unlikely to result in patch conflicts, so I don't think it needs to be split.\n\nThe only change that is needed is to replace \"Intel, Inc\" with \"Intel Corporation\" in the files that have it.  This could be done by hand, or by fixing the updatecw.sh script (but only if fixing the script doesn't take much effort, I expect this to be a one-time issue).",
